<title>UK: Pilkington drops as meeting disappoints.</title>
<headline>Pilkington drops as meeting disappoints.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-07-24</dateline>
<text>
<p>Shares in UK glass and plastics group Pilkington Plc eased on Thursday in heavy trade after a disappointing annual general meeting with shareholders, dealers said.</p>
<p>Pilkington shares dropped a penny to 130p by 1314 GMT in volume of around 8.8 million shares.</p>
